 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7242b92e6280>([29])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7242b92e6280> = [[1, 29], [1, 29, 1], [29], [29, 1], [1, 29], [1, 29, 1], ...].count
 +  and   3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7242b92e6280>([1, 29])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7242b92e6280> = [[1, 29], [1, 29, 1], [29], [29, 1], [1, 29], [1, 29, 1], ...].count
 +  and   2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7242b92e6280>([29, 1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7242b92e6280> = [[1, 29], [1, 29, 1], [29], [29, 1], [1, 29], [1, 29, 1], ...].count
